1015
01:30:32,700 --> 01:30:35,200
We'll settle up later.
First let me see.

1016
01:30:35,400 --> 01:30:38,500
- Yes.
- I'll let you know in time.

1017
01:30:39,600 --> 01:30:42,200
God bless you, Father.

1018
01:30:43,200 --> 01:30:44,600
Yes.

1019
01:31:14,600 --> 01:31:15,600
Excuse me.

1020
01:31:30,600 --> 01:31:33,000
- Mother of Jesus.
- Pray for him.

1021
01:31:33,000 --> 01:31:35,500
- Mother of divine grace.
- Pray for him.

1022
01:31:35,600 --> 01:31:37,500
- Tower of David.
- Pray for him.

1023
01:31:37,600 --> 01:31:39,500
- Tower of ivory.
- Pray for him.

1024
01:31:39,600 --> 01:31:41,700
- House of gold.
- Pray for him.

1025
01:31:41,800 --> 01:31:43,300
- Heaven's gate.
- Pray for him.

1026
01:31:43,400 --> 01:31:45,500
- Refuge for sinners.
- Pray for him.

1027
01:31:45,600 --> 01:31:47,100
- Consolation of the afflicted.
- Pray for him.

1028
01:31:47,300 --> 01:31:49,400
- Aid for Christians.
- Pray for him.

1029
01:31:49,600 --> 01:31:51,500
- Queen of angels.
- Pray for him.

1030
01:31:51,700 --> 01:31:53,500
- Queen of the apostles.
- Pray for him.

1031
01:31:53,600 --> 01:31:55,700
- Queen of the patriarchs.
- Pray for him.

1032
01:31:55,800 --> 01:31:57,700
- Queen of all the saints.
- Pray for him.

1033
01:31:57,700 --> 01:31:59,900
- Queen of the apostles.
- Pray for him.

1034
01:31:59,900 --> 01:32:01,700
- Queen of prophets.
- Pray for him.

1035
01:32:01,800 --> 01:32:04,400
They found Lucas in a canyon.

1036
01:32:05,600 --> 01:32:08,800
Three years ago they killed
his father and two brothers.

1037
01:32:08,800 --> 01:32:10,900
Chato Aguilar's men.

1038
01:32:11,200 --> 01:32:13,600
What about the municipal guards?

1039
01:32:13,700 --> 01:32:15,700
They help them.

1040
01:32:17,000 --> 01:32:21,000
But someone should be told.
The authorities.

1041
01:32:21,800 --> 01:32:24,200
If you only knew of all
we've accomplished.

1042
01:32:24,900 --> 01:32:28,000
Things are settled differently
around here. Don't worry.

1043
01:32:29,700 --> 01:32:31,800
Can I ask you a moral question?

1044
01:32:34,800 --> 01:32:38,900
Well, I don't know a lot about
moral theology, but...

1045
01:32:39,600 --> 01:32:41,000
Ask away.

1046
01:32:45,100 --> 01:32:46,700
What do you think about abortion?

1047
01:32:49,600 --> 01:32:52,500
We don't have that problem
around here.

1048
01:32:53,200 --> 01:32:55,500
But in your parish you do, huh?

1049
01:33:03,000 --> 01:33:06,800
I don't know. In some cases,
one would have to consider it.

1050
01:33:09,300 --> 01:33:10,500
Yes.

1051
01:33:22,600 --> 01:33:25,700
And how is the bishop?

1052
01:33:29,700 --> 01:33:33,100
Look, he sent you a fax.

1053
01:33:35,900 --> 01:33:38,700
It's a suspension <i>ad divinis</i>
against you.

1054
01:33:41,200 --> 01:33:43,300
And excommunication too.

1055
01:33:53,800 --> 01:33:56,400
You are out of the church now, Natalio.

1056
01:33:58,800 --> 01:34:02,300
You can't officiate,
or give the sacraments anymore.

1057
01:34:03,500 --> 01:34:06,700
You have to go before the bishop.

1058
01:34:07,900 --> 01:34:09,400
No...

1059
01:34:10,300 --> 01:34:12,600
...l'm not going before anyone.

1060
01:34:17,300 --> 01:34:18,900
Out of the church.

1061
01:34:21,500 --> 01:34:24,300
If they want to kick me out,
I'm already here.

1062
01:34:24,300 --> 01:34:27,000
I'll stay on as just another peasant.

1063
01:34:27,700 --> 01:34:29,700
I chose this path.

1064
01:34:30,900 --> 01:34:32,000
And you?

1065
01:34:42,000 --> 01:34:44,000
Believe me, I admire you, Natalio.

1066
01:34:51,000 --> 01:34:52,700
Well, I have to go.

1067
01:35:35,800 --> 01:35:38,700
Holy Virgin among virgins...

1068
01:35:41,100 --> 01:35:45,600
...don't let me fall,
or lose my way in adversity.

1069
01:35:47,800 --> 01:35:49,800
I have been your faithful son...

1070
01:35:52,000 --> 01:35:54,500
...since I was a child.

1071
01:35:56,800 --> 01:35:59,700
You have protected me along
the path of duty.

1072
01:36:01,100 --> 01:36:03,500
Do not forsake me in this crucial hour.

1073
01:36:03,600 --> 01:36:06,700
My Mother, grant me a miracle, please.

1074
01:36:07,900 --> 01:36:10,100
Save me, Holy Mother.

1075
01:36:13,200 --> 01:36:15,200
My mother called from Mexico City.

1076
01:36:15,300 --> 01:36:18,200
- What happened?
- They've operated on Father Benito.

1077
01:36:18,700 --> 01:36:20,900
They'll be back in two weeks.

1078
01:36:21,300 --> 01:36:22,800
That's good.

1079
01:36:29,600 --> 01:36:33,900
What you told me over the phone,
I thought about it.

1080
01:36:36,800 --> 01:36:38,100
No.

1081
01:36:39,200 --> 01:36:41,200
No. Think about it more.

1082
01:36:42,100 --> 01:36:44,800
You have to do it of your own free will.

1083
01:36:52,300 --> 01:36:54,600
Heaven purify my soul.

1084
01:36:54,600 --> 01:36:59,000
My spirit is filled with emotion when
I contemplate the blessings of my Lord.

1085
01:36:59,300 --> 01:37:01,300
You have shed your light
on your servant...

1086
01:37:01,300 --> 01:37:04,200
Grant me a miracle, Holy Mother.

1087
01:37:04,300 --> 01:37:05,600
Save me.

1088
01:37:14,900 --> 01:37:17,500
Friday at 2 in the morning.

1089
01:37:17,700 --> 01:37:20,300
Bring double the amount
that you gave me.

1090
01:37:44,900 --> 01:37:47,000
Right on time, Father.

1091
01:37:47,100 --> 01:37:49,000
As you should be.

1092
01:37:51,200 --> 01:37:53,000
And the girl?

1093
01:37:54,000 --> 01:37:56,600
Don't tell me she chickened out?

1094
01:37:59,600 --> 01:38:01,400
Too bad, Father.

1095
01:38:58,800 --> 01:39:00,800
Straight ahead, straight ahead.

1096
01:39:01,400 --> 01:39:04,400
Take the next turnoff to the left.

1097
01:39:38,200 --> 01:39:39,900
It's all very clean.

1098
01:39:40,100 --> 01:39:41,900
It's a hospital.

1099
01:39:43,800 --> 01:39:47,400
- Wait. I want to talk to the doctor.
- You can't go in.

1100
01:39:47,400 --> 01:39:48,700
I'll take care of it.

1101
01:39:48,800 --> 01:39:50,800
- I have to see the place.
- No.

1102
01:39:50,900 --> 01:39:52,400
The money.

1103
01:39:55,700 --> 01:39:58,000
Come, come, Amelita.

1104
01:39:59,000 --> 01:40:00,900
Everything will be fine.

1105
01:40:02,900 --> 01:40:04,500
Ask God to watch over you.

1106
01:40:12,500 --> 01:40:14,200
Pray for me, okay?

1107
01:40:16,900 --> 01:40:19,200
Come, Amelia, come.

1108
01:40:19,400 --> 01:40:20,900
Come, child.

1109
01:40:26,800 --> 01:40:28,600
I'll be here, I'll be here.

1110
01:41:03,200 --> 01:41:05,100
Good evening, young man.

1111
01:41:05,400 --> 01:41:09,100
- Good evening.
- Don't you remember me?

1112
01:41:09,800 --> 01:41:13,000
- No.
- We met on a bus.

1113
01:41:14,200 --> 01:41:17,000
When we were held up, remember?

1114
01:41:18,000 --> 01:41:19,200
Oh, yes.

1115
01:41:19,500 --> 01:41:23,400
I always remember
how good you were.

1116
01:41:23,400 --> 01:41:26,900
There aren't people like that,
anywhere.

1117
01:41:27,000 --> 01:41:30,800
I couldn't open the store
with my grandson, like I told you.

1118
01:41:30,700 --> 01:41:33,800
I wandered around and around.

1119
01:41:33,900 --> 01:41:38,500
Until I got a job here as a night
watchman and handyman.

1120
01:41:38,500 --> 01:41:42,100
- Here at the hospital?
- That's what they call it.

1121
01:41:43,400 --> 01:41:45,800
You came for them
to relieve your girlfriend?

1122
01:41:50,000 --> 01:41:52,000
I came for them to relieve me.

1123
01:41:52,100 --> 01:41:54,600
Don't worry. They all come out okay.

1124
01:41:54,600 --> 01:41:56,400
Screwed, but content.

1125
01:41:58,400 --> 01:42:00,000
God willing.

1126
01:42:00,800 --> 01:42:03,200
A hemorrhage! It won't stop!

1127
01:42:03,300 --> 01:42:04,700
What?

1128
01:42:09,500 --> 01:42:13,000
We're treating her, get out!
You can't take her!

1129
01:42:12,900 --> 01:42:15,100
- Out of my way!
- She'll bleed to death!

1130
01:42:15,200 --> 01:42:16,200
Wait!

1131
01:42:16,400 --> 01:42:18,600
She's bleeding to death.

1132
01:42:19,800 --> 01:42:21,500
Go straight.

1133
01:42:21,700 --> 01:42:23,100
- In Santa Marta...
- Open it.

1134
01:42:23,100 --> 01:42:27,000
...there is a good hospital.
- Yes, I know, doctor.

1135
01:42:35,100 --> 01:42:38,800
I have to go. I have to go!

1136
01:42:41,200 --> 01:42:43,700
Take me, take me!

1137
01:42:45,300 --> 01:42:48,100
Take me!

1138
01:42:48,500 --> 01:42:51,300
Christ, sanctify me!
Body of Christ, save me!

1139
01:42:51,400 --> 01:42:54,400
Passion of Christ, comfort me!
Blood of Christ, intoxicate me!

1140
01:42:54,600 --> 01:42:56,600
Good Jesus, hear me!

1141
01:43:05,300 --> 01:43:07,200
I don't want to die.

1142
01:43:08,300 --> 01:43:11,900
You won't die. You won't die.

1143
01:43:18,000 --> 01:43:24,500
<i>Thy two breasts are like two young roes</i>
<i>That are twins...</i>

1144
01:43:33,300 --> 01:43:35,400
Wait, Amelita, wait for me.

1145
01:43:45,500 --> 01:43:46,800
Wait, Amelita.

1146
01:44:02,200 --> 01:44:03,400
Amelita?

1147
01:45:01,300 --> 01:45:04,900
Poor little girl. Imagine that.

1148
01:45:04,900 --> 01:45:05,900
What happened?

1149
01:45:06,500 --> 01:45:10,100
Well, it turns out that Ruben...

1150
01:45:10,100 --> 01:45:12,900
...Don Paco's son, got her pregnant.
Imagine that.

1151
01:45:13,500 --> 01:45:14,900
What a bastard.

1152
01:45:16,200 --> 01:45:20,500
Well, the poor thing was desperate.

1153
01:45:20,500 --> 01:45:23,900
She went to one of those horrid clinics
to get rid of the baby.

1154
01:45:25,500 --> 01:45:28,300
Father Amaro, who is a saint...

1155
01:45:28,300 --> 01:45:31,100
...I don't know how he did it,
went to save her.

1156
01:45:31,300 --> 01:45:32,400
Did he save her?

1157
01:45:33,600 --> 01:45:37,700
He got her out of there and took her
to a hospital in Santa Marta.

1158
01:45:38,100 --> 01:45:41,900
But the poor thing had already
bled to death.

1159
01:45:42,100 --> 01:45:43,300
And she died?

1160
01:45:43,600 --> 01:45:46,600
Yes, she died.

1161
01:45:47,400 --> 01:45:49,000
How awful.

1162
01:45:49,700 --> 01:45:55,800
Gordo, you have to close those
clinics down. Today, okay?

1163
01:47:00,300 --> 01:47:04,000
The holy sacrifice of mass
which we celebrate today...

1164
01:47:03,900 --> 01:47:07,800
...we offer for the soul
of our dear sister Amelia.

1165
01:47:07,800 --> 01:47:11,200
Lord grant her eternal rest...

1166
01:47:11,400 --> 01:47:14,800
...and may His perpetual light
shine upon her.

1167
01:47:14,800 --> 01:47:17,400
In the name of the Father,
the Son and the Holy Ghost.

1168
01:47:17,500 --> 01:47:18,900
Amen.

1169
01:47:19,100 --> 01:47:22,100
- The Lord be with you.
- And with your spirit.

1170
01:47:22,100 --> 01:47:25,400
The grace of our Lord Jesus...

1171
01:47:25,400 --> 01:47:27,400
...the love of the Father...

1172
01:47:27,400 --> 01:47:30,400
...and the communion of the Holy Ghost
be with you all.

1173
01:47:30,500 --> 01:47:32,500
And with your spirit.

1174
01:47:33,900 --> 01:47:36,800
- I confess...
- I confess...

1175
01:47:36,900 --> 01:47:41,900
...before God almighty and before you,
brothers...

1176
01:47:41,800 --> 01:47:43,900
...that I have sinned greatly...

1177
01:47:44,000 --> 01:47:48,500
...in thought, word, deed
and by omission.

1178
01:47:48,500 --> 01:47:53,400
For my faults, my faults,
my great faults.

1179
01:47:53,400 --> 01:47:56,900
For these I pray to Holy Mary,
always Virgin...

1180
01:47:57,000 --> 01:48:00,100
...and the angels and the saints...

1181
01:48:00,700 --> 01:48:03,200
...and all of you, my brothers...

1182
01:48:03,800 --> 01:48:07,000
...who intercede for me
before God our Lord.

